c0361d02-34e0-4e01-ba26-d926930238bd.01471d92-3928-4ab0-95dd-8dcb99795d93.description=
Check to see if the value stored in a specified flow variable, denoted by key, is null.

Inputs\:
keyName - The key to check, i.e. the name of the flow variable.

Returns\: 
The value in the specified key, i.e. flow variable.

Responses\:
isNull - If the key is a null pointer, i.e. the flow variable doesn't have an assigned value.
notNull - If some value is stored in the key, i.e the flow variable has a value assigned.

c0361d02-34e0-4e01-ba26-d926930238bd.cf507998-e335-48bf-b0b7-b7d45a143532.description=This workflow adds/ updates the component properties to Instance using Artifact APIs. onlyUpdate\: yes/no yes - To update values of existing properties no - To add and/or update properties keyValuePairs\: If you want to Add/update new properties\: property1 PUBLIC INTEGER 5 property2 PUBLIC STRING abc xyz If you want to only update the values of existing properties\: property1 5 property2 abc xyz c0361d02-34e0-4e01-ba26-d926930238bd.description=
This flow updates cpu and memory values on the component.

Inputs\:
componentId		\: Component Id
userIdentifier	\: User Identifier
nCPU		\: Number of CPUs
memory		\: Memory (MB)
nCPU_deployed	\: CPUs Deployed
memory_deployed	\: memory Deployed 


Response\:
success - The operation completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.
no more - there are no more results to retrieve.
